Class ListingEntity

java.lang.Object
com.uninaswap.server.entity.ListingEntity
Direct Known Subclasses:
AuctionListingEntity, GiftListingEntity, SellListingEntity, TradeListingEntity
@Entity public abstract class ListingEntity extends Object
Abstract base class for all types of listings in the UninaSwap platform
